{"article_id":"DX8h79qZqFZIlpfv","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Republicans are ripping into Democrats and media outlets","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"for what they allege is silence over the latest development in the sexual assault allegation against presumptive Democratic nominee Joe Biden","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"-- after video emerged","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"that appears to show accuser Tara Reade ' s mother","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"referring to the alleged assault on TV in 1993 .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"\" Joe Biden isn ' t sheltering in place in his basement bunker","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"because of the pandemic ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"he ' s hiding from Tara Reade , \"","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Donald Trump Jr. tweeted Friday .","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"CNN SLAMMED FOR TREATMENT OF BIDEN SEXUAL ASSAULT ALLEGATIONS","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"AFTER OLD LARRY KING CLIP SURFACES","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Trump Jr. later took a shot at the New York Times for a profile piece of Biden","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"published Saturday","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"that made no reference of the allegations against him .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"\" Shockingly , the words 'Tara Reade ' are nowhere to be found in this @ nytimes puff piece on creepy @ JoeBiden ' s campaign .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"But don ' t worry guys ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"there ' s a lot of tough reporting in here","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"like Joe","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"having dinner with his wife","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"and going on bike rides ! \"","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Reade , a staffer for Biden in 1993","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"who has claimed","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"he sexually assaulted her ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"told Fox News on Friday","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"that it was her mother","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"who called into \" Larry King Live \" in the resurfaced clip","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"and alluded to her daughter ' s experience on Capitol Hill .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Biden ' s campaign has adamantly denied the accusation .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"The Intercept on Friday first reported the transcript on the Aug. 11 , 1993 broadcast ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"where the woman","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"-- who does not mention sexual assault , or the specific details of Reade ' s claim --","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"asks a question to the panel .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"The clip was later found","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"and published by Newsbusters .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"`` Yes , hello .","depth":4},{"id":36,"text":"I ' m wondering","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"what a staffer would do","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"besides go to the press in Washington ?","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"My daughter has just left there ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"after working for a prominent senator ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"and could not get through with her problems at all ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"and the only thing","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"she could have done","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"was go to the press ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"and she chose not to do it out of respect for him , ''","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"the caller says .","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"BERNIE AIDES ERUPT OVER DEVELOPMENT IN BIDEN SEXUAL ASSAULT CLAIM","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"AS DNC STAYS MUM","depth":4},{"id":49,"text":"`` In other words , she had a story","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"to tell","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"but , out of respect for the person","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"she worked for ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"she didn ' t tell it ? ''","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"King inquires .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"`` That ' s true , ''","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"the woman responds","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"before King cuts away to a panel","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"to discuss her claim .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"`` This is my mom .","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"I miss her so much and her brave support of me , ''","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"Reade tweeted about her mother ,","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"who died in 2016 .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"The Biden campaign referred Fox News to a statement earlier this month from Biden Deputy Campaign Manager Kate Bedingfield","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"that said :","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"\" What is clear about this claim :","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"it is untrue .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"This absolutely did not happen . '' `` Vice President Biden has dedicated his public life","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"to changing the culture and the laws around violence against women , ''","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Bedingfield said .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"`` He authored and fought for the passage and reauthorization of the landmark Violence Against Women Act .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"He firmly believes","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"that women have a right","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"to be heard","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"- and heard respectfully .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"Such claims should also be diligently reviewed by an independent press . ''","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"But Republicans have zoned in on what they see as a lack of aggressive media coverage , of the same kind","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"that accusations against Supreme Court Justice Brett Kavanaugh and President Trump received .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"\" CNN gave airtime to [ Kavanaugh accuser ] Christine Blasey Ford 's attorneys , her friends , her family .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"They even aired focus groups on the allegations , \"","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"RNC Chairwoman Ronna McDaniel said.","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"\" It ' s been 24 hrs","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"since evidence from CNN own 's archive emerged","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"corroborating Tara Reade 's story .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"\" How in the world can CNN justify not mentioning it ? \"","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"Trump Jr. quote retweeted a tweet from the Kavanaugh hearings","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"in which House Speaker Nancy Pelosi praised Ford ' s bravery .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"\" Far too few people are recognizing Tara Reade ' s sheer bravery","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"in sharing her story today .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"That * must * not be overlooked , \"","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Trump Jr. said .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"\" Now we ' ll see","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"if a different set of rules still applies to Joe Biden , \"","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"Erin Perrine , the principal deputy communications for President Trump 's re-election campaign , said in a statement to Fox News .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"\" Maybe now at least one reporter will ask him about it . \"","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"The development has also seen criticism of Democrats from the left of the party ,","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"who also accused fellow Democrats of ignoring the claims","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"because it involves Biden .","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"`` The video of Tara Reade 's late mother","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"calling into Larry King","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"to blow the whistle about about","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"[ sic ]","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"Tara 's sexual assault","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"is being met with relative silence from a cadre of progressives right now","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"and I want you all to know","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"that I see you , ''","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"former Sanders senior adviser Winnie Wong tweeted .","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"`` We all do . ''","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":215,"left":154,"right":214,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":116,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent"